<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<p><strong>Q. Where do I pick up/drop off my costumes?</strong></p>
<p>A. We are home based business located at 50 Kraft Drive Kitchener.</p>

<p><strong>Q. What sizes do you carry?</strong></p>
<p>A. We carry a wide variety of sizes from infant to adult. Many of our costumes come from consignors we may have more selection in certain sizes.</p>

<p><strong>Q.How long is the rental period?</strong></p>
<p>A. To make life simpler for the renters, we have chosen to allow you to keep the costume until from before Halloween until Saturday November 8th. </p>

<p><strong>Q. What if I cannot come during the regular hours?</strong></p>
<p>A. Email us and we will do our best to set up an appointment for you.</p>

<p><strong>Q. How do I consign costumes?</strong></p>
<p>A. Check out the Consignor page.</p>

<p><strong>Q. How are payments made?</strong></p>
<p>A. Payments can be made online with PayPal or in person.  When making payment with PayPal for rental items, your credit card will be authorized for the rental amount plus a deposit but you will only be changed for the rental amount when the costume is returned as long as it is returned within 29 days.  Cash deposits for rentals will be returned upon receipt of costume.</p>

<p><strong>    Q. How does your referral program work? </strong></p>
<p>A. Have three people who rent or buy from NH Costumes refer you upon their purchase and we will contact you to let you
know that you have earned a free costume rental!   </p>

<p>If you have any additional questions please <a href="Contact.aspx">Contact Us</a>.  </p>
